    30→## Using `mdbook` as a library
    32→The `mdbook` binary is just a wrapper around the underlying mdBook crates,
    33→exposing their functionality as a command-line program. If you want to
    34→programmatically drive mdBook, you can use the [`mdbook-driver`] crate.
